    narr:narration """This hub aggregates strategic-alignment assessments, where the prevailing consensus identifies a [high degree of strategic coherence](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment) across the corpus. Documents are frequently characterized as being the strategy itself rather than mere artifacts of it, with [positioning theses](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment_GTM) and [mission-vision anchors](narr:RubricAssess_strategic_alignment) serving as the primary connective tissue. The narrative is consistently reinforced through [Git-native AI memory](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment_1) and [narrative architecture principles](narr:Assess_Strategy_collective_memory), which prioritize auditability and provenance. Strategic execution is further validated through [ADR-based decision rationales](narr:RubricAssess_Strategy_ADR001) and [IP-crisis-driven positioning](narr:Assessment_StrategicAlignment_IPCrisis). While the dominant thread emphasizes a unified, narrative-driven roadmap, assessments also highlight the [operationalization of these principles](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment_GTM) into specific GTM and architecture domains. The thematic span extends from [high-level worldview-as-product claims](narr:RubricAssess_StrategicAlignment) to granular [architecture-domain alignment](narr:Assess_Strategy_cm) and [customer-architect value exchange](narr:Assessment_StrategicAlignment_CustomerArchitect).""" ;
